<p class="ql-align-center">蓬莱人炫富新方式</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200819/5a76150ec2dc4c85b0993692d38137a3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200819/344e627c3178472c95a19678c0c18c36.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
